history.content:
Online Faculty Advising for CS-Intended Students

Monday 4/13 at 3-4pm 
Zoom link: https://berkeley.zoom.us/j/114765318  
 
Are you looking for help from a faculty perspective to choose your Fall 2020 schedule? Or are you looking for advice regarding industry or research? This semester Professor Gireeja Ranade will be hosting an online Faculty Advising session for CS-intended students. Join us!
